   "source": [
    "# Behind the Drop: Revenue & Customer Analytics for a Corporate Travel Platform | SQL Reference Notebook\n",
    "\n",
    "**Objective:** Understand what is driving booking volume drops, identify booking loss patterns, and surface recommendations for leadership.\n",
    "\n",
    "**Dataset:** 300,000 booking records across Air, Hotel, and Car from a corporate travel management platform — full year 2018.\n"
   ]
